{"tid":1331882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急！求救！要人！] 集中721文宣討論區 勿被分化！","createTime":"2019-07-19T06:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T06:49:40.000Z","uid":83699,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e67b658006706ec4db0ac143a09103ba5eed7f48","tid":1331882,"uid":83699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:02:08.000Z","msg":"由於連登尚有岩岩加入嘅成員<br />\n我認為現在有必要同各位新會賢講下<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登現正被分化</span></span><br />\n五年前雨傘運動失敗導致民主路程不進反退<br />\n係因為反建制派互相割蓆<br />\n割到最後大家根本有心無力<br />\n成個議會連最後嘅三份一議席都搶走<br />\n可想而知鼓吹割蓆同篤灰<br />\n只會將運動推向滅亡<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但今次我地終於成功引領全港二百萬人走埋一齊<br />\nWe Connected<br />\n<br />\n懇請大家遺忘所有分化post! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由6月頭一開始到依家<br />\n我地根本乜都無爭取過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係無呀！</span></span><br />\n去到今日 d三毛騎劫post出晒黎<br />\n後日就係721 <br />\n成立臨時立法會嘅討論去晒邊？<br />\n準備打仗嘅情緒同氣氛去晒邊？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化不割蓆不篤灰</span></span><br />\n先係呢場民主運動嘅維持到咁耐嘅核心<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n勇武嘅勇武 和理嘅和理 文宣嘅文宣<br />\n只要幫到前線幫到義士<br />\n邊個都可以係主角<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得有問題危害到前線嘅放上黎<br />\n解決完就end post<br />\n每個人都有機會做錯<br />\n唔好係呢刻追究邊個<br />\n邊個做唔做到野大家心照<br />\n我地要嘅係團結一致<br />\n利用二百萬+五人嘅力量<br />\n去爭取翻屬於我地嘅民主<br />\n<br />\n再一次重申<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721 不分化不割蓆不篤灰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香城online wiki<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/1/d/16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4/htmlview?sle=true#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fu%2F1%2Fd%2F16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4%2Fhtmlview%3Fsle%3Dtrue%23&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=a0b2cdf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/1/d/16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4/htmlview?sle=true#</a><br />\n<br />\n香城online懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gU0qsqF0_qg9f-vF9BKu3zZ2rfz5pxtuz57PY2Vo30M/edit#gid=1765855472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1gU0qsqF0_qg9f-vF9BKu3zZ2rfz5pxtuz57PY2Vo30M%2Fedit%23gid%3D1765855472&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=97602300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gU0qsqF0_qg9f-vF9BKu3zZ2rfz5pxtuz57PY2Vo30M/edit#gid=1765855472</a><br />\n<br />\n[721] 和理非之所以企出嚟 唔係想勇武以死相博 而係想大家一齊凱旋歸來<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dkBgNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dkBgNS</a><br />\n<br />\n[7.21] 同我推返哂721上熱門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dkeybS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dkeybS</a><br />\n<br />\n【香城OL wiki】史上最全攻略！！持續更新！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dkgKdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dkgKdS</a>"},{"pid":"ed6f31514dceaa094d27fb9dd78a30aca9b6e8e2","tid":1331882,"uid":2612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGEm7kx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGEm7kx.png&h=84eef868&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VR1gWdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVR1gWdS.png&h=e9b1febb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4w4Y9yT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4w4Y9yT.png&h=5088c22f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Print 出黎痴係連儂牆比老人家知<br />\n<br />\nAirdrop 比人</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2584e318f3f433aa065c272442b4